The Monster & VOAs (core Moonshine sources)
These are the foundational texts for Monstrous Moonshine:

Borcherds — construction of the Monster Lie algebra; proof of Moonshine.
Frenkel–Lepowsky–Meurman — construction of the Moonshine module 𝑉♮.
Conway–Norton — original Moonshine conjectures.
Tuite — uniqueness of the Moonshine module.
Zhu — modular invariance of VOA characters.

These are the “sun” behind the Monster’s “moonlight.”
